---

<section class="flex min-h-screen items-center justify-center px-6 pt-16">
  <div class="max-w-2xl text-center">
    <!-- 状态标签 + 动效 -->
    <span class="reveal inline-block rounded-full border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-500/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-blue-400">
      🟢 Available for work
    </span>

    <h1 class="mt-6 text-5xl font-bold leading-tight text-white sm:text-6xl reveal reveal-delay-1">
      你好，我是<span class="text-gradient"> [你的名字]</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-400 reveal reveal-delay-2">
      一个热爱技术、喜欢创造的开发者。专注于构建优雅、高效的 Web 应用，
      享受从零到一的创造过程。
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center gap-4 reveal reveal-delay-3">
      <a
        href="#contact"
        class="rounded-lg bg-blue-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white transition hover:bg-blue-500 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-blue-500/25"
      >
        联系我
      </a>
      <a
        href="#projects"
        class="rounded-lg border border-gray-700 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 transition hover:border-gray-500 hover:text-white"
      >
        查看作品
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
